<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">The Service Weapon</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Jesse Faden finds herself unexpectedly participating in a test of her worthiness to become the new Director of the Federal Bureau of Control - by being nudged into picking up the ex-director's Service Weapon and plunged into the Astral Plane, with the warning that failing will result in the weapon blowing her head off.	</p>
